Given:
```scala
class ScalaColls(n: Int) {  
  Array.fill(n)(null)
}
```

This compiles under:

 * Scala 2.9.2, with and without -optimize, with and without the REPL
 * Scala 2.10.0-SNAPSHOT, without the REPL, or with the REPL but without -optimize

The glorious crash dump runs like this:
